<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''咪康唑'''（Miconazole）是一種[[抗真菌药|抗真菌药]]，可用於治療[[皮癬菌病|皮癬]]、[[花斑癬|花斑癬]]，或是皮膚及陰道[[念珠菌症|念珠菌感染]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。該藥物可用於治療{{tsl|en|tinea corporis|體癬}}、[[股癣|股癣]]、[[足癣|足癣]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。該藥物通常以外用藥膏劑型，塗抹於患處皮膚或陰道<ref name=AHFS2016>{{cite web|title=Miconazole Nitrate|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/miconazole-nitrate.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|access-date=8 December 2016|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221013013/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/miconazole-nitrate.html|archive-date=21 December 2016}}</ref>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
常見副作用包含塗抹部位搔癢<ref name=AHFS2016/>。[[妊娠|妊娠]]期間用藥應屬安全<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book| vauthors = Hamilton R |title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition |date=2015 |publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning |isbn=9781284057560 |page=180 }}</ref>。本品屬於[[咪唑|咪唑]]類藥物<ref name=AHFS2016/>，可抑制真菌[[麦角固醇|麦角固醇]]的合成，影響真菌[[細胞膜|細胞膜]]的製造<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

<!-- History and culture -->
本品於1968年獲得專利，並於1971年獲准用於醫藥用途<ref name=Fis2006>{{cite book| vauthors = Fischer J, Ganellin CR |title=Analogue-based Drug Discovery|date=2006|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9783527607495|page=502|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA502|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220144314/https://books.google.ca/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA502|archive-date=2016-12-20}}</ref>。本品列名於[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]之中<ref name="WHO21st">{{cite book | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | title = World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list 2019 | year = 2019 | hdl = 10665/325771 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | id = WHO/MVP/EMP/IAU/2019.06. License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO | hdl-access=free }}</ref>。

== 適用症 ==
咪康唑可以外用於治療腳癬（俗稱香港腳）、環癬（金錢癬、轮癣）、股癣（骑师癣），內用於治療口腔鵝口瘡（口腔念珠菌症）、陰道鵝口瘡（念珠菌阴道炎）。此外其口服凝膠也可用於治療唇部障碍口角炎。

